WEBVTT

00:05.874 --> 00:06.580
Stan!

00:06.682 --> 00:09.116
What are you doing with my fancy jam?!

00:09.218 --> 00:10.151
I'm getting an iguana.

00:10.252 --> 00:11.586
What are you talking about?

00:11.687 --> 00:13.487
Duh! I need the jar for my crickets.

00:15.591 --> 00:17.758
The guy at the pet store
wouldn't sell me the iguana

00:17.859 --> 00:19.760
until I could show him
a big jar of crickets...

00:19.861 --> 00:22.663
to prove I could feed the iguana...
I think.

00:22.798 --> 00:24.432
I was so excited I
just ran out of there.

00:24.533 --> 00:26.133
Stan, you jerk!

00:26.235 --> 00:29.670
That was the jam I got
at Colonial Williamsburg!

00:29.771 --> 00:33.274
Now I have to go back,
and it's <i>so</i> boring!

00:34.021 --> 00:35.776
Well, if something's
that important to you,

00:35.877 --> 00:37.445
maybe put a note on it!

00:37.546 --> 00:39.480
Oven's clean.

00:39.581 --> 00:41.849
I feel like I'm always
screwing up with Francine.

00:41.950 --> 00:44.452
- You are. That's accurate.
- Gets me tense.

00:44.553 --> 00:46.854
- I feel like I'm wound so tight.
- You are.

00:46.955 --> 00:48.556
You're like a wire that's been wound

00:48.657 --> 00:50.391
around a thing super tight.

00:50.492 --> 00:52.226
That's me. You're telling my story.

00:52.327 --> 00:53.494
You got to cut loose.

00:53.595 --> 00:55.630
Cutting loose. That's the dream.

00:55.731 --> 00:57.031
Well, let's do it.

00:57.132 --> 00:58.933
You're my boy,
and I'm always here to help.

00:59.034 --> 01:00.635
Sorry, I'm kind of down to the dregs,

01:00.736 --> 01:01.969
but we'll make it work.

01:02.405 --> 01:04.305
To cutting loose.

01:04.406 --> 01:05.539
♪ Loose ♪

01:05.641 --> 01:07.208
♪ Cut loose ♪

01:07.309 --> 01:09.877
♪ Let us drink some more booze ♪

01:09.978 --> 01:11.045
♪ Wow ♪

01:11.146 --> 01:12.647
♪ Oh, wow ♪

01:12.748 --> 01:15.549
♪ Chug this blue CuraÃ§ao ♪

01:15.651 --> 01:18.219
♪ Lis... terine ♪

01:18.320 --> 01:20.988
♪ It's a booze 'cause it's green ♪

01:21.089 --> 01:22.823
♪ Quaker Stake ♪

01:23.027 --> 01:24.292
Whoa, whoa, whoa. Whoa, whoa, whoa.

01:24.393 --> 01:26.160
I have a better idea.

01:26.261 --> 01:28.129
We can drink this.

01:28.230 --> 01:31.332
It's got a... a note on it.

01:31.433 --> 01:32.833
Ho, ho, ho!

01:32.934 --> 01:34.335
I'm Santa.

01:34.436 --> 01:37.071
You should get coal, but it's wine.

01:40.609 --> 01:42.176
I think it's happening.

01:42.277 --> 01:44.345
I'm loose.

